  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You momentarily tap into the powers of the Rinnegan, adjusting time and space to undo a foolish move on your part. When you miss with an attack roll, the creature is immune to the damage you dealt, or a creature succeeds on a saving throw against a Jutsu, Feature, or Ability you used, you can rewind your personal timeline, regaining the action you spent to perform the action.</p><p data-start=\"381\" data-end=\"652\" data-is-only-node>Any resources you used for the action, such as chakra or Ki, remain spent, but you regain the action itself. This ability allows you to correct a critical failure and continue your battle with a chance to redo your approach, though the cost remains for whatever was used.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
    "source": {
      "custom": ""
    },
    "activation": {
      "type": "reaction",
      "cost": 1,
      "condition": "(Which you take when a you miss an attack roll, the target is immune to the damage you dealt, or a creature succeeds on a saving throw you have them make.)"
